author: Fextralife
description:
Elden Ring Nightreign BEST STARTING SKILLS & How To Use Them
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, I'm going to be talking about the starter skills, the skills that each character starts with, as well as the skills that you can put on with relics. We're gonna be going through how each of these works. I'm going to be telling whether you should use it or not, and hopefully get some good information out of this video.

Elden Ring Nightreign Wiki: https://eldenringnightreign.wiki.fextralife.com/Elden+Ring+Nightreign+Wiki
